<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC7">
<l>kaṇṭu koṇṭu eṉṉaik kārimāṟappirāṉ</l>
<l>paṇṭai valviṉai pāṟṟi aruḷiṉāṉ</l>
<l>eṇṭicaiyum ariya iyampukēṉ</l>
<l>oṇtamiḻc caṭakōpaṉ aruḷaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Karimārapirāṉ saw and took me in,</l>
<l>[he] graciously removed [my] previous bad karma.</l>
<l>I proclaim so that all the eight quarters know</l>
<l>the grace of Caṭakōpaṉ, the [master of] bright Tamiḻ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
